sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n侏儒得罪你地啲咩<br />\n點解唔比我地享受世界第一嘅榮譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f2e1a225017b1d168362a7e9f9aa459d72f633","tid":432872,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"我唔直接答你 用例子答<br />\n<br />\n殘奧會分級"},{"pid":"e1658bdebb3916266a19d70702a1e21e307f3643","tid":432872,"uid":152701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔直接答你 用例子答<br />\n<br />\n殘奧會分級</blockquote><br />\n未分到咁仔細<br />\n無考慮殘疾人士中 <br />\n有啲腿長啲 有啲腿短啲<br />\n對我呢啲腳短嘅侏儒來講唔公平<br />\n我都希望可以好似星如咁做世界冠軍<br />\n證明香港嘅侏儒運動員唔係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85029622395202384e78b910db762e0494ac90a4","tid":432872,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔直接答你 用例子答<br />\n<br />\n殘奧會分級</blockquote><br />\n你係咪話殘障先會分級別比賽 你串鳩呀如呀？"},{"pid":"35eec6d6956ec0aede457c077bad257f7542bc7a","tid":432872,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔直接答你 用例子答<br />\n<br />\n殘奧會分級</blockquote><br />\n你係咪話殘障先會分級別比賽 你串鳩呀如呀？</blockquote><br />\n減磅走線稱王既野<br />\n你識條春咩<br />\n夠膽上台頂阿如一拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d969027139ccccc81dcb4eeb1a100312b6f6de","tid":432872,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔直接答你 用例子答<br />\n<br />\n殘奧會分級</blockquote><br />\n你係咪話殘障先會分級別比賽 你串鳩呀如呀？</blockquot